snippet.textDisplay: Few songs actually take you to the deepest depths of your heart and then take away a part of it. “Fasle” is one of the most painful song. It tells you that the most important and most difficult part of love is to let it go. ❤️‍🩹 Those who have been fortunate enough to be in love and those who have ever loved will understand and feel this song. Each and every word is written with a lot of love, pain, and tears.
